        public CachingClassLoaderConfiguration with(String requestQueue,
                                   String responseQueue)
        Specifies the request and response queue names that should be used for classloading.
        Parameters:
        requestQueue - The name of the queue where class loading requests will be sent and received.
        responseQueue - The name of the queue where class loading responses will be sent and received
        Returns:
        The current instance of CachingClassLoaderConfiguration to continue configuration.

      • with

        public CachingClassLoaderConfiguration with(CacheType cacheType,
                                   boolean shareCache)
        Specifies the cache configuration to use for optimizing amount of requests.
        Parameters:
        cacheType - The type of the cache that server should use to not issue same requests multiple times.
        shareCache - The boolean flag that indicates whether the cache should be shared between different requests (true) or not (false)
        Returns:
        The current instance of CachingClassLoaderConfiguration to continue configuration.
